{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-217-balanced-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 217: Jednaki brojevi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pozitivan ceo broj sa $k$ cifara (za decimalne brojeve) naziva se jednak ako je zbir njegovih prvih cifara $⌈\\frac{k}{2}&#x3C;0xE2>&#x3C;0x8C>&#x3C;0x89>$ jednak zbiru njegovih poslednjih cifara $⌈\\frac{k}{2}&#x3C;0xE2>&#x3C;0x8C>&#x3C;0x89>$, gde se $⌈x&#x3C;0xE2>&#x3C;0x8C>&#x3C;0x89>$, nazivan kao plafon (ili \"ceo deo\") $x$, predstavlja najmanji ceo broj $≥ x$, stoga je $⌈π&#x3C;0xE2>&#x3C;0x8C>&#x3C;0x89> = 4$ i $⌈5&#x3C;0xE2>&#x3C;0x8C>&#x3C;0x89> = 5$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, sve palindrome su jednaki, kao što je 13722.</p>\n<p>Neka je $T(n)$ suma svih brojeva manjih od $10^n$.</p>\n<p>Dakle: $T(1) = 45$, $T(2) = 540$ i $T(5) = 334\\,795\\,890$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $T(47)\\pmod{3^{15}}$</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4461000cf542c50ff58","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301859,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-217-balanced-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function balancedNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nbalancedNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>balancedNumbers()</code> treba da vrati <code>6273134</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(balancedNumbers(), 6273134);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedNa